parameters:
\N<Rozaro>So this is the entrance to the lowest level of the ruins
where Zeda has taken refuge.

\N<Rozaro>I've warned repeatedly, but I've heard there are many traps
from here on. Perhaps Zeda has set up something as well, we
should proceed with caution.

\N<Rozaro>Also... this is something from when I was in the same unit
as him, but it seems he was secretly conducting his own
research on Mind Lyuda.

\N<Rozaro>Both you and I are standing here now, benefiting from that
Mind Lyuda.

\N<Rozaro>He knows full well the effects of that secret medicine. We
can't predict what he'll do next, it's better to be
cautious.

\N<Rozaro>What's been going on with you since earlier? You seem off.
Are you listening to me?

\N<Segi>Could you please... stay a bit further away from me...? I...
I'm just...

\N<Rozaro>...Is it that black robe that's bothering you? That you have
to dress so indecently in front of me.

\N<Rozaro>Segi-san, I'm here to save Riia's life. I understand how you
feel, but now is not the time...

\N<Segi>I... understand my role... and I believe I understand that
you're here for Riia's sake...

\N<Rozaro>Then why are we having such a vulgar conversation about
what's embarrassing or not at this point?

\N<Segi>Rozaro-san... we've been through a lot together. But now, I
want to trust you when you say you're doing this for Riia.

\N<Segi>No, please let me trust you. I don't want to hate or doubt
anyone anymore...

\N<Segi>So... for that reason, to allow myself to trust you... could
you please remove your hand that's touching me right now...?

\N<Rozaro>...Understood. In return, will you also understand that
there's no ulterior motive in my actions this time?

\N<Rozaro>Indeed, you and I have had our share of past events. But
now, can you promise to avoid antagonizing me for Riia's
sake as well?
